      "1\u2264ui,vi\u2264N1 \\leq u_i, v_i \\leq N1\u2264ui\u200b,vi\u200b\u2264N",
      "1\u2264Ai\u22641061 \\leq A_i \\leq 10^61\u2264Ai\u200b\u2264106.",
      "The sum of NNN over all test cases won't exceed 5\u22c51045\\cdot 10^45\u22c5104."
